Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:28.61,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&HC16721&}Airplane  飞到天空的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.66,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&HC16721&}话语屈于心中  即将爆发出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:41.25,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&H000000&}想说出来  {\c&HA34CEE&}藏在心中的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:48.30,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&HA34CEE&}说不出来  不知该怎么表达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:56.47,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&HA34CEE&}直到最后我还是无法坦率起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:00.39,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&HA34CEE&}故意将联系你我的纽带
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:06.40,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\c&HC16721&}纠缠起来  {\c&HA34CEE&}切断开来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:13.41,lrcc2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在航迹云渐渐模糊消失之前
